# Camera Trigger Survey Mission
# Automated aerial photography mission with distance-based camera triggering
# Author: Patrick Kelly (@Kuscko)
# Version: 1.0
# Last Updated: 2026-02-03
#
# Mission: Grid survey with camera triggering every 50m
# Area: 300m x 300m
# Altitude: 100m AGL
# Camera trigger: Distance-based (50m intervals)

